Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:59.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Welcome to ProSeka AfterTalk: "Grow Glorious Grow" edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm Rina Honnizumi, the voice of Momojan's Shizuku Hinomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:22.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This ProSeka AfterTalk is a program where we look back on the event story and enjoy the AfterLive together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:27.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This time, we're covering the "grow glorious grow" event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:35.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The event just ended a moment ago, but did you all check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:36.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:41.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'll be keeping an eye on the comments, so please join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:48.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I actually jotted down some notes earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:54.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,about things I really wanted to talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.70,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,so I'm hoping to go over those with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I was just so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:03.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Both for MMJ and for Shizuku, they've overcome so many hurdles,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:07.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and even though she'd already grown wings and taken flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,she's still surpassing herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Her growth just never stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's honestly so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:21.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Please post your thoughts on the event or the stream using the hashtag #ProSekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:25.62,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The staff have set up the YouTube chat so I can see it right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.38,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,so I'll be picking out comments that catch my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.86,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:35.98,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The staff have provided me with a device again today,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:42.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,so I'd like to look back at the story and the member illustrations with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:50.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Also, I'll be creating a private room to watch the AfterLive together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:57.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'll share the Room ID at 21:55, so I'll let you know then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:12:01.50,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Please get your devices ready so we can watch it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:03.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I hope you'll all join in!
Comment: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.28,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Let's get started!
Comment: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:14.02,Shizuku,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Story Watchalong ===
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:14.02,Shizuku,host_meta,0,0,0,,Now then, I'd like to look back on the story of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:19.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,"Grow Glorious Grow," but first, I want to watch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,one episode together with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Just one episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.01,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I think
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,opinions might be split,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:29.84,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,just a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:36.84,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Actually, I was thinking I'd like to see Episode 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,What do you all think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:41.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Please let me know in the comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:46.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Oh, you're already saying "7"! Everyone is so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:47.66,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:52.06,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,So Episode 7 is good? 7 it is. I'll go with your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:53.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:58.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Alright, let's watch Episode 7 together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:00.69,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm the one who has to play it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:03.74,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have said "here you go."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.50,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'll start it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:09.38,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:25.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,"I won't lose!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:30.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Hagiyama-chan is seriously such a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:33.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:38.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:40.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That's as far as we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:44.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That was the moment they recognized each other as rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:49.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And that was Episode 7. We watched it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:50.38,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It went by so fast!
Comment: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:51.72,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:51.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And that's as far as we'll watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:59.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Actually, I really love the part that comes after this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:02.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,where everyone is at Momo House watching the commercial that finally aired,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:03.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and we see Saito-san's reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:11.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I also love seeing Minori-chan getting all pure and excited, squealing over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:12.10,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,But that's all for the clips.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for watching with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:19.26,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I have so much I want to say, but we need to watch the live show at 10:55 PM,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:23.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,so everyone, please keep an eye on the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:29.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I might just keep talking without noticing the time, but I really want to chat,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.64,0:22:32.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,so I'll talk as much as time allows.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:35.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Where should I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:38.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:48.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I have a few favorite scenes that weren't in the episodes we just watched, so let's review.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.44,0:22:56.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Hagiyama-san from Rewrite, who was in the commercial, previously appeared in the Idol Lovers festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.36,0:23:02.34,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She's a member of a wonderful unit that seems like they'll have a good rivalry with Momojan,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.34,0:23:11.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and it was great to see them meet like that. But here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:14.70,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,she appears again as Shizuku's rival while they're co-starring as models.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:21.46,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,They're both stepping up their game, and I'm really looking forward to seeing them both in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:23.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Also, regarding Shizuku's past...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:32.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,There were several flashback scenes. I can't remember exactly which episode numbers they were,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:42.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,but I'd love for everyone to go back and watch them. A junior member from her Cheerful＊Days era appears to greet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.08,0:23:54.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Back then, Shizuku was being produced as a mysterious idol and was completely overwhelmed with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:24:01.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It was a really painful time for her, but she was trying her absolute best. And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:06.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,this new junior member joined. She had worked so hard to join because she looked up to her seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:11.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,There's a scene where she tells Shizuku directly that she's going to do her best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.56,0:24:15.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,At that time, Shizuku was already...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.08,0:24:21.94,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She was feeling really down, thinking she wasn't suited to be the center of Cheerful＊Days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:28.74,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,But by meeting that junior, she realized she was carrying the future of those girls on her shoulders too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.74,0:24:35.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She decided that if she lacked confidence, she had to polish herself until she finally found it.
Comment: 0,0:24:35.00,0:24:35.50,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.00,0:24:35.50,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.92,0:24:39.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,this was also a fated encounter, with her junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.44,0:24:43.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's a scene that really moved me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.36,0:24:47.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and one of my favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.84,0:24:52.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Also, the Momojan members... after Shizuku
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.28,0:24:56.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,passed the audition,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.08,0:25:01.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,she was practicing all by herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.92,0:25:05.74,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and they brought her some refreshments.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.74,0:25:10.42,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That's also depicted in the card stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.42,0:25:11.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,that specific
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.60,0:25:14.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,sense of distance between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.84,0:25:25.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Airi especially knows Shizuku well from her Cheerful Days era,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.12,0:25:35.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,so she can tell how serious Shizuku is without a single word. Airi doesn't even say anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.64,0:25:42.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,she just watches over her. It really makes me realize
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.36,0:25:47.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,what wonderful girls the Momojan members are.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.52,0:25:54.30,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Shizuku was like a tightly wound string,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.30,0:25:56.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,there was so much tension.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.32,0:26:12.46,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It felt a bit precarious, but Airi was happy to see the Shizuku who was the center of Cheerful Days again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.46,0:26:14.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's so emotional, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.32,0:26:19.90,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,But Airi also knows that Shizuku suffered back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.90,0:26:21.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She doesn't say it to her face, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.52,0:26:29.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,but she's watching over her growth, including all of that. That's their relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.60,0:26:34.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I was honestly thinking, "Thank you so much for writing this,"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.12,0:26:37.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,while we were recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.32,0:26:43.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Looking at the comments... everyone's saying "trust."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.84,0:26:44.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That's it exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.76,0:26:51.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,In the second part of Shizuku's side story...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.44,0:27:01.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,everyone is thinking about what they can do for Shizuku and taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.00,0:27:11.10,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Since she was being so stoic with her diet, they brought her high-nutrition, low-fat
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.10,0:27:15.30,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,meals as refreshments. That's true love, honestly.
Comment: 0,0:27:15.30,0:27:16.24,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.30,0:27:16.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's all about supporting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.28,0:27:18.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I mean... I should probably talk about it a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.12,0:27:20.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.84,0:27:24.23,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,What should I talk about...
Comment: 0,0:27:27.52,0:27:29.12,Shizuku,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Song Watchalong ===
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.52,0:27:29.47,Shizuku,host_meta,0,0,0,,So, that Grand Fleur commercial...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.71,0:27:35.05,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That live shot of Shizuku doing the recording...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.36,0:27:39.02,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,What did you think of it, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.02,0:27:46.82,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,When I record for the game, I usually record my lines alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.82,0:27:57.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It seems Hagiyama-san had already finished her voice recording, but we had some lines to say in unison.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.40,0:28:03.62,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,There was a line where Hagiyama-san and Shizuku say "Grand Fleur" together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.62,0:28:11.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Normally, for lines in unison, they play the previously recorded voice into my headphones,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.08,0:28:16.98,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and I listen to that while recording my part to match the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.98,0:28:23.58,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That's the usual way we get those nice synchronized lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.58,0:28:24.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,But get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.16,0:28:26.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I recorded that without listening at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.52,0:28:29.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And yet, it was so perfectly in sync!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.84,0:28:37.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I was so surprised. I only saw the finished version at the same time as all of you, so I was amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.92,0:28:45.34,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I got an "OK" right away. I thought I might have to redo it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.34,0:28:51.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,but I guess Hagiyama-chan and Shizuku were just naturally on the same wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.88,0:28:55.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I can't believe that actually happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.60,0:29:01.70,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The lines were actually quite long, too, like "The new Floraison Éclat..."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.70,0:29:06.22,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I actually looked up what kind of color "Floraison Éclat" was.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.22,0:29:08.60,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It seemed like a really beautiful floral color.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.44,0:29:11.54,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.54,0:29:13.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad everyone is saying they were wowed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.44,0:29:19.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I feel like that's really rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.88,0:29:28.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It makes me happy that these two, who met as good rivals, could be so in sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.12,0:29:37.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I hope they continue to push each other to new heights with the girls from ReLight.
Comment: 0,0:29:37.44,0:29:38.12,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.68,0:29:43.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Let's keep talking a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.96,0:29:53.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm going back to talking about the flashback scenes again,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.62,0:30:00.82,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,but it was when Shizuku was searching for what it was she was lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.82,0:30:11.70,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It was around the scene where Miku-chan calls out to her when Shizuku decides to watch some old footage in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.70,0:30:20.10,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,In that scene where she watches footage from her Cheerful Days era, there are lines from the past Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.10,0:30:21.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She's was muttering to herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.76,0:30:25.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,"I need to do it more like this..."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.60,0:30:32.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,We actually recorded several different patterns for that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.40,0:30:36.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And we picked out the very best one for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.36,0:30:43.58,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,As for the patterns... there was one where she sounded more precarious,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.58,0:30:48.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,like a Shizuku who makes you worried just by looking at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.08,0:31:04.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She was really cornering herself, thinking she had to master the dance to carry the weight of being the center of Cheerful Days.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.19,0:31:05.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She felt like there was no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.80,0:31:11.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,We recorded a few patterns of that desperate Shizuku, and I felt like...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.64,0:31:18.74,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Well, we've seen Shizuku cornered like this a few times before,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.74,0:31:23.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,but it's been a while since she went that far. It was actually quite tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.28,0:31:26.14,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and there were several scenes that were pretty painful to record.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.14,0:31:37.10,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Flashbacks to her Cheerful Days era always involve lines where she's pushing herself too hard, which is painful for me too,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.10,0:31:41.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,but that Shizuku is what leads to the Shizuku we have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.64,0:31:44.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I thought having that gap would create more of a sense of drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.47,0:31:46.97,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That's what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.36,0:31:49.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.76,0:31:55.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,A cornered Shizuku has a certain charm to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.24,0:31:56.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.64,0:32:03.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Especially since she was being promoted as the "mysterious Shizuku" back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.12,0:32:06.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and she never showed that side of her effort to anyone.
Comment: 0,0:32:07.72,0:32:16.72,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.72,0:32:16.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seeing how she kept working so hard in silence behind the scenes,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.72,0:32:20.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,it really makes you feel how lonely she was, doing her absolute best all on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.12,0:32:25.84,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And that connects back to the story about her juniors I mentioned earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.72,0:32:29.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,where Shizuku feels like she has to work hard
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.00,0:32:33.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,for their sake as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.77,0:32:35.49,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.49,0:32:38.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thinking about it that way, I'm so glad she met Momojan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.80,0:32:42.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, Minori,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.80,0:32:43.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Haruka,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.32,0:32:45.18,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and Airi...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.18,0:32:46.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That's really how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.61,0:32:48.11,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.84,0:32:54.58,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's about time for me to get ready for the AfterLive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.58,0:33:01.82,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'll reveal the room ID around 10:55, so everyone, please get your devices ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.82,0:33:02.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.60,0:33:05.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,We'll all join at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.56,0:33:10.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'll be careful not to make any mistakes with the controls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.00,0:33:15.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Creating the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.57,0:33:20.07,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.92,0:33:27.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Now I'll write down the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.72,0:33:28.41,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.41,0:33:30.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm not showing them yet, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.20,0:33:32.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'll show them to you all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.00,0:33:35.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Please have your devices ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.88,0:33:38.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It'll be around 10:55.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.36,0:33:48.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Oh, it won't fit here, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.89,0:33:49.50,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.50,0:33:50.11,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.64,0:33:52.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,There are six digits in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.71,0:34:08.21,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:34:09.28,0:34:10.76,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.28,0:34:10.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I managed to write it down without any mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.84,0:34:13.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Is everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.64,0:34:14.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.88,0:34:19.58,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Type it in and enter on the count of three!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.58,0:34:23.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Space is limited, so it'll be first-come, first-served.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.92,0:34:25.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.32,0:34:30.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I really want us all to get hyped together!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.04,0:34:31.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's the first time everyone's hearing this song, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.76,0:34:33.70,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.70,0:34:37.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's my first time seeing it too, how amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.00,0:36:36.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The AfterLive starts at 10:00 PM!
Comment: 0,0:36:37.80,0:36:43.40,Shizuku,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Card Illustrations ===
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.80,0:36:43.40,Shizuku,host_meta,0,0,0,,I'm planning to introduce the cards today, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.40,0:36:44.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Just a moment ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.04,0:36:47.46,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.46,0:36:58.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I saw the illustration used for Shizuku's banner this time and thought, "Wait, is this really the untrained version?"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.60,0:37:01.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The quality is high enough to be a trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.52,0:37:02.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It really shocked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.56,0:37:07.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Actually, I got a look at it during the voice recording session.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.76,0:37:10.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This is how Shizuku looks this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.03,0:37:11.53,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And man,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.84,0:37:14.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,it was just incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.92,0:37:15.82,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I even started clapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.82,0:37:16.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.56,0:37:20.46,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I really wish they'd actually sell these cosmetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.46,0:37:23.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This is just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.32,0:37:24.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.80,0:37:34.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,We've seen cool versions of Shizuku in a few events before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.40,0:37:38.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,there's a different sparkle in her eyes this time, a real sense of her strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.84,0:37:44.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,You can really see all of Shizuku's hard work reflected in her expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.92,0:37:46.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She looked so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.76,0:37:49.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And the trained illustration is amazing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.56,0:37:56.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,You can see her looking like she's about to take flight into the blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.88,0:37:59.84,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at the cards together later.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.84,0:38:01.58,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,They're incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.58,0:38:02.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The outfits are cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.92,0:38:06.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's like a hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.64,0:38:09.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,A hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.08,0:38:15.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The script says it's a studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.88,0:38:18.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.88,0:38:29.34,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I thought the set really fit the concept this time. It feels very mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.34,0:38:36.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,But since they wanted to attract a younger audience than Grand Fleur's usual target demographic...
Comment: 0,0:38:36.68,0:38:41.40,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.68,0:38:41.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This time, Hagiyama-chan and Shizuku were featured,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.40,0:38:46.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and they fit the concept so perfectly that it just made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.68,0:38:55.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,ProSeka really shows us so many different sides of the characters,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.32,0:38:56.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,they really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.52,0:38:59.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, speaking as a fan myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.64,0:39:03.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,showing such a wide range for the characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.60,0:39:06.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I bet there were people who literally fell out of their chairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.68,0:39:07.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.64,0:39:08.57,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.57,0:39:10.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,You'd definitely fall off. This one is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.28,0:39:11.74,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's honestly mind-blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.74,0:39:13.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.60,0:39:18.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It was even trending on X, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.16,0:39:24.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I thought, "This must be for ProSeka," when the banner was revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.20,0:39:27.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I happened to be looking at X right at that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.96,0:39:34.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and when the official account posted the image of Shizuku's banner for this event,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.96,0:39:37.84,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,everyone reacted so strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.84,0:39:40.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It made me happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.12,0:39:43.22,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's almost time to start, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.22,0:39:44.82,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,About 10 seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.82,0:39:46.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.08,0:39:47.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.80,0:39:51.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm going to enjoy this with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.16,0:39:51.71,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.32,0:39:53.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.00,0:47:46.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,.
Comment: 0,0:47:48.08,0:47:50.44,Shizuku,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Song Watchalong ===
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.08,0:47:50.44,Shizuku,host_meta,0,0,0,,So, what did everyone think?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.32,0:47:56.34,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Yuuyu-san wrote this new song for Momojan,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.34,0:47:57.90,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,"Hashiru".
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.90,0:47:58.63,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.92,0:48:01.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Shizuku says,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.68,0:48:05.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,"Look at me."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.88,0:48:10.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She's never been this strong before.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.32,0:48:13.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's so deeply moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.00,0:48:14.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I seriously started crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.64,0:48:18.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,In the lyrics for the chorus,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.24,0:48:22.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,it says, "Can you tell who the lead is?"
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.92,0:48:25.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She's asking everyone to look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.16,0:48:34.50,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I feel like... earlier, Shizuku mentioned that since joining MORE MORE JUMP!, she's been relying on everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.50,0:48:39.54,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,or rather, she described it as "spoiling herself."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.54,0:48:45.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,But that's definitely not a bad thing; it's a form of progress for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.80,0:48:54.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,However, she chose to call it "spoiling herself" and decided to aim for even greater heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.09,0:48:55.59,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.36,0:49:01.50,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Yuuyu-san wrote a song and lyrics that perfectly symbolize that growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.50,0:49:04.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Yuuyu-san, thank you so much, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.84,0:49:14.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Once it's added to the game, I really want you to pay attention to the lyrics. How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.20,0:49:15.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.92,0:49:23.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,After the first chorus, there's a solo section where everyone comes to the center one by one, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.20,0:49:27.02,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Wasn't that just incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.02,0:49:33.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The part where Shizuku comes to the center and turns around...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.72,0:49:39.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I really felt like the choreography and formations were just god-tier.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.72,0:49:43.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The lighting, the stage... and the outfits too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.00,0:49:45.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The outfits were amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.76,0:49:47.38,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.38,0:49:54.02,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I mentioned the cards briefly, but you can see it in the cards too, so later, let's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.02,0:49:55.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,show them some love, seriously.
Comment: 0,0:49:55.64,0:49:57.88,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.64,0:49:57.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, thank you for all the comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.88,0:49:59.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Everyone's crying a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.52,0:50:01.78,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I totally get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.78,0:50:02.60,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.60,0:50:04.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The outfits were so cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.80,0:50:07.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,They really catch your eye, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.32,0:50:13.53,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's a song that really makes me excited for Momojan's future,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.53,0:50:14.06,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.06,0:50:14.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.92,0:50:26.78,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And with that, the 3DMV was just uploaded to the official ProSeka YouTube channel at 10:10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.78,0:50:28.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's already live!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.20,0:50:30.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Please go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.04,0:50:34.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Well, since you're here, I'd love for you to stay and watch the rest of this stream with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.88,0:50:37.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and then you can go watch the MV as many times as you want afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.96,0:50:40.84,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,But if you really want to see it right now, go ahead and watch it,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.84,0:50:43.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,seriously. I'm so excited for the 3DMV!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.04,0:50:43.71,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.71,0:50:45.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Please check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.04,0:50:47.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Haruka, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.64,0:50:49.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.56,0:50:53.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we can deliver another new song to everyone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.08,0:50:59.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,So, there are five members in total who were newly added this time.
Comment: 0,0:50:59.68,0:51:03.44,Shizuku,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Card Illustrations ===
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.68,0:51:03.44,Shizuku,host_meta,0,0,0,,Did everyone check out the illustrations and side stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.44,0:51:06.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at the members right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.76,0:51:08.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.96,0:51:10.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.44,0:51:12.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,First up is Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.04,0:51:16.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This is the trained art...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.92,0:51:18.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Here is the trained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.92,0:51:23.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Isn't the vibe of this outfit just incredible?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.92,0:51:26.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She's really taking flight, for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.40,0:51:29.38,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I love the expression Shizuku has as she looks back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.38,0:51:31.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I think everyone can relate to this feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.32,0:51:35.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,You can really feel her strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.56,0:51:41.38,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And these... should I call them banners? These flags...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.38,0:51:43.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Can you tell they're shaped like wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.04,0:51:51.82,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,On the left side... in the story, there was that swan metaphor,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.82,0:52:00.74,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,about how they look elegant above the water but are paddling like crazy underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.74,0:52:05.78,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That's exactly like Shizuku. I really love that metaphor,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.78,0:52:12.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and this illustration really makes me think of that. It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.36,0:52:15.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Next, here is the untrained version.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.24,0:52:16.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This is the banner card.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.28,0:52:22.42,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This is insane. It appeared in the story earlier, and I was so shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.42,0:52:24.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Look at Shizuku here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.16,0:52:25.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She's sparkling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.28,0:52:30.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The level of expression just keeps going up and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.16,0:52:34.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And the cosmetics Shizuku is holding in her right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.64,0:52:38.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I seriously want this new product for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.76,0:52:41.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She's just too beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.08,0:52:43.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I could look at this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.04,0:52:44.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.80,0:52:47.70,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Maybe I should use this makeup as a reference.
Comment: 0,0:52:47.70,0:52:49.78,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.70,0:52:49.78,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.78,0:52:51.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Okay, just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.20,0:52:55.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Zoom in a bit... By the way, Shizuku looks a bit more mature today,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.80,0:52:59.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,so I actually had my own look done a bit more maturely too.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.52,0:53:04.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I can't help but be conscious of it when Shizuku is drawn so beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.28,0:53:06.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.00,0:53:07.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's Shizuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.00,0:53:11.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Next is Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.32,0:53:14.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The trained art...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.56,0:53:15.94,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She's bursting with energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.94,0:53:23.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I love Minori-chan's jumps. She's always the one bouncing around the most during lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.28,0:53:25.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,that girl. She really is Momojan.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.40,0:53:30.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Minori-chan's jumping power and her full effort really reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.56,0:53:33.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,They really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.91,0:53:38.41,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.61,0:53:40.11,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.20,0:53:43.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This angle is just irresistible.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.08,0:53:45.14,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It is. Everyone, look at the shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.14,0:53:46.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,There are wings on the heels of the shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.82,0:53:48.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.32,0:53:52.84,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I can really feel the incredible attention to detail in the small things.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.40,0:53:54.60,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.60,0:53:59.34,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The designs are slightly different for each member, so I can't help but look closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.34,0:54:02.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.08,0:54:08.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Wait, seriously, we just saw Episode 7, but looking at the story after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.64,0:54:18.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,this... this is that expression she makes when they all watch the aired Grand Fleur commercial together.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.56,0:54:25.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And this sort of... look on Airi-chan's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.12,0:54:27.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.28,0:54:30.78,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Minori-chan, thank you so much, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.78,0:54:31.43,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Comment: 0,0:54:32.16,0:54:37.04,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.16,0:54:37.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Also, this background... it's the Momo House.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.00,0:54:41.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I've never seen the Momo House from this angle before.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.56,0:54:42.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This illustration...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.48,0:54:47.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seeing it like this makes the Momo House feel so cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.52,0:54:52.70,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Next up is... MIKU.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.70,0:54:57.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,You can really feel a strong sense of determination from this MIKU.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.16,0:54:59.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.32,0:55:07.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,MIKU really shows so many different expressions depending on how strong her will is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.56,0:55:11.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This time, it's almost like she's carrying Shizuku's resolve right along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.32,0:55:19.06,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,MIKU stayed close to Shizuku this time, supporting her with such a wonderful sense of distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.06,0:55:25.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Shizuku was able to overcome it because MIKU supported her. She's truly a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.92,0:55:26.47,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.47,0:55:27.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.84,0:55:29.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,MIKU looks so cool too.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.92,0:55:31.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She looks so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.88,0:55:32.63,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.20,0:55:36.54,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I really love this cool MIKU too.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.54,0:55:37.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.24,0:55:40.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you for all the comments, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.96,0:55:45.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And here is the untrained art of MIKU and Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.80,0:55:50.38,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This is from that scene... wait, not that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.38,0:55:51.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This is the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.20,0:56:02.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's the two of them watching the old footage of Shizuku practicing her dancing, like Shizuku mentioned earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.16,0:56:07.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's MIKU staying close to her while they check the screen together.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.20,0:56:08.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I love the distance between them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.72,0:56:11.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She's watching over her from so close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.40,0:56:18.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This scene is exactly that... where she tells her that the old Shizuku
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.36,0:56:30.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,is also the same Shizuku she is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.24,0:56:41.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Shizuku watches her old self and says, "It doesn't feel like me," but MIKU tells her, "This is you too, Shizuku."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.24,0:56:45.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's such a heartwarming scene.
Comment: 0,0:56:45.16,0:56:48.00,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.16,0:56:48.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It really shows that she's not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.92,0:56:51.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,MIKU, thank you for always supporting her, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.20,0:56:52.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.56,0:56:55.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It makes me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.40,0:56:57.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Moving on...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.52,0:57:02.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Here is Haruka-chan's trained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.40,0:57:05.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She's sitting down in this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.76,0:57:06.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.08,0:57:09.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This one also shows her watching over Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.48,0:57:12.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.20,0:57:16.14,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Everyone understands Shizuku so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.14,0:57:17.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Well, they all understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.24,0:57:22.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Units are just so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.28,0:57:29.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Shizuku is here because of everyone, and everyone is here because of Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.52,0:57:32.84,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.92,0:57:35.42,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Really... always.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.42,0:57:36.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I can't stop saying thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.24,0:57:40.60,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This white clover is nice too, and the three-leaf motif.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.96,0:57:53.66,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The coloring is a bit different every time, and this time it's all unified with a blue sky, as if to cheer on Shizuku as she takes flight. This blue really suits her.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.66,0:57:54.84,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's like Haruka's color.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.60,0:57:58.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.96,0:58:07.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Personally, I like the shorts. Shizuku has different lengths on her left and right legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.36,0:58:11.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This... what you'd call the "absolute territory," this part right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.44,0:58:13.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.04,0:58:13.74,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.74,0:58:14.39,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.64,0:58:16.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.32,0:58:18.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Haruka-chan looks great in shorts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.20,0:58:20.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She's truly amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.08,0:58:24.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This illustration is just...
Comment: 0,0:58:24.88,0:58:27.34,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.88,0:58:27.34,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This is... this one is the untrained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.34,0:58:28.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Haruka is...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.60,0:58:37.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,making this highly nutritious, low, low-calorie meal for Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.44,0:58:38.60,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.40,0:58:44.30,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Haruka-chan is such a stoic girl who works so hard on her diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.30,0:58:52.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,so she's naturally very knowledgeable about food and nutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.36,0:58:56.60,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I actually learn a lot myself
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.15,0:58:57.65,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,just by reading the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.28,0:59:04.58,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Like, 'this is a bit high in fat,' or 'this is a sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.58,0:59:07.42,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,you can eat even on a low-carb diet.'
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.42,0:59:13.74,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm like, 'Oh, I see,' and I even use it as a reference sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.74,0:59:18.82,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Physical health... food is the foundation of your physique,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.82,0:59:19.51,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,it starts with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.04,0:59:21.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Building your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.68,0:59:26.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Haruka-chan supports Shizuku in ways like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.52,0:59:28.74,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.74,0:59:33.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,These colorful vegetables look great, they look delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.52,0:59:37.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And then, Airi.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.08,0:59:41.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,For Airi-chan, we only have the untrained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.08,0:59:42.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.84,0:59:45.24,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,When you think of Airi-chan, you think of the midriff look.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.17,0:59:46.67,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's a classic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.72,0:59:50.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Airi-chan is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.00,0:59:52.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That wink!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.08,0:59:57.90,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It really gives you a burst of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.90,0:59:58.84,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,it really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.96,1:00:02.58,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,When it comes to Airi-chan, you can't go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.58,1:00:03.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.52,1:00:08.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, really...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.36,1:00:11.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we could look at these together just now.
Comment: 0,1:00:12.77,1:00:13.27,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.77,1:00:13.27,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.16,1:00:20.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And with that, we've seen all the cards for this event.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.84,1:00:21.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.68,1:00:25.60,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Someone mentioned this in the comments earlier, but for this time...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.60,1:00:26.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.88,1:00:27.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The team name.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.88,1:00:29.94,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I made it "Fabulous."
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.94,1:00:33.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It really is fabulous. That's the only word for it, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.07,1:00:34.57,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.08,1:00:37.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.80,1:00:42.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, let me talk a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.52,1:00:47.74,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I touched on this earlier, but how far did I get?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.74,1:00:50.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Right, I talked about my favorite scenes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.40,1:00:55.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And about the achievement of our voices syncing up in the "Grand Fleur" commercial.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.72,1:00:56.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.80,1:00:57.30,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.52,1:01:11.34,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,In this story, when Shizuku was facing the "Grand Fleur" audition, she saw Hagiyama-chan's performance.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.34,1:01:18.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She saw that powerful light of hers and realized, "This is what I'm lacking." There was a scene like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.44,1:01:26.22,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I really empathized with Shizuku on that point.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.22,1:01:32.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,In my own daily activities,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.36,1:01:35.84,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,there are so many times when I'm faced with my own shortcomings.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.36,1:01:42.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm aware that I'm lacking things and I run into those walls,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.20,1:01:47.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,but I don't know specifically what I should do to grasp what's missing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.68,1:01:48.41,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.41,1:01:49.60,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.36,1:01:55.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Honestly, I could even call this one of my life's biggest challenges.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.04,1:02:02.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm very blessed with my environment, and the people around me are all so charming and...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.00,1:02:04.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,just wonderful people.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.72,1:02:09.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Because of that, they have things that I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.95,1:02:10.45,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,In other words...
Comment: 0,1:02:12.04,1:02:16.28,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.04,1:02:16.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,They shine so brightly and have charms that I don't have.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.36,1:02:23.66,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And when I'm struggling like that, I imagine being in the deep sea,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.66,1:02:32.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,struggling in the dark where I can't see what's ahead. It's just so painful.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.00,1:02:37.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's like everything you do backfires, or you just don't see any results.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.88,1:02:43.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Maybe some of you feel the same way too.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.47,1:02:45.14,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.14,1:02:46.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,There are times when it's just so painful.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.88,1:02:47.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.52,1:02:55.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,there's a moment when you suddenly realize, "This is it..."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.16,1:02:59.14,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Like, "This is what I was looking for all along."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.14,1:03:05.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's strange, but you only understand it once you've actually found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.56,1:03:14.94,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I'm not explaining this well, I'm struggling to find the right words,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.94,1:03:16.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,but in my experience...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.40,1:03:22.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,there's something you only realize once you find that light, like "Oh, this was it."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.68,1:03:29.10,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,You can't see it while you're struggling; only the "you" who found it can know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.10,1:03:31.64,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,So for those of you
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.20,1:03:45.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,who might be struggling right now, it might be hard, but one day that light will be in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.32,1:03:45.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That moment
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.56,1:03:48.74,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,will definitely come. Truly.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.74,1:03:50.02,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That's just how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.02,1:03:55.49,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I want this to be a world where that light is already within reach.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.49,1:03:56.13,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.20,1:04:02.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That's a theme I personally wanted to convey through this story,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.28,1:04:08.88,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and through Shizuku as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.88,1:04:10.60,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,So let's both keep doing our best.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.60,1:04:18.04,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Whether it's club activities, work, or job hunting,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.04,1:04:24.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I know things can be tough. In those times, I hope you'll look at ProSeka stories,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.08,1:04:27.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,take a little break, and listen to lots of the songs.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.72,1:04:33.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'd be so happy if they could be a source of strength or healing for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.36,1:04:39.34,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,When you lack confidence... Shizuku was like that too, wasn't she?
Comment: 0,1:04:39.34,1:04:55.56,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.34,1:04:55.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Shizuku was happy to pass the "Grand Fleur" audition, but she didn't know what she needed to do to reach a level worthy of performing alongside Hagiyama-san,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.56,1:04:57.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,so facing the actual performance like that is so scary.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.76,1:05:05.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It's terrifying to have to face the wall in front of you when you know you're still lacking something.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.28,1:05:12.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That fear from a lack of confidence was a scene I really empathized with.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.32,1:05:16.32,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Also, also, there's this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.32,1:05:16.95,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.20,1:05:32.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Shizuku felt Hagiyama-chan's unyielding will to never lose or back down during her performance,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.40,1:05:40.10,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,and during the costume fitting, Hagiyama-chan asked Shizuku what she was thinking about during the audition.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.10,1:06:04.12,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to give a performance that would surpass her opponent, which really struck a chord. I'm lucky to go to many auditions, but I get so nervous that I put a lot of pressure on myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.12,1:06:10.70,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And since it's such a wonderful project, I worry about whether I...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.70,1:06:17.38,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...might hold the production back, if I can do it well, or if I'll be a burden to my co-stars.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.38,1:06:18.78,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,All these different thoughts go through your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.78,1:06:26.02,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,There are times when I feel like I'm going to be crushed by those feelings, but in those moments, if I had that will to never lose
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.02,1:06:32.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,or back down, I felt like I could stand much firmer as myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.48,1:06:35.54,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Hagiyama-chan is seriously so strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.54,1:06:36.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.36,1:06:40.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I ended up learning a lot too, just like Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.36,1:06:41.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.88,1:06:49.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I felt like if I had a heart that strong, I might even grow wings myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.20,1:06:51.18,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'd take flight, just like Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.18,1:06:52.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'll do my best too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.52,1:06:54.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm counting on your support!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.08,1:06:56.16,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to share.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.96,1:06:58.06,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I learn so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.06,1:07:00.82,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, the ProSeka stories...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.82,1:07:02.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,...really teach me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.44,1:07:06.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,They've become a source of emotional support for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.84,1:07:07.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.52,1:07:14.06,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'd be so happy if it resonated with all of you as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.06,1:07:14.71,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,.
Comment: 0,1:07:15.64,1:07:17.72,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.64,1:07:17.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Everyone's telling me, "Let's do our best!"
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.72,1:07:18.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.20,1:07:20.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, together.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.92,1:07:22.05,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Supporting each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.05,1:07:22.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.56,1:07:24.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you for all your support.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.76,1:07:25.48,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'll do my best too.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.16,1:07:29.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,In my heart, I'm always right there with Shizuku.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.20,1:07:29.70,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.16,1:07:34.02,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,So, I don't have any regrets left.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.02,1:07:37.67,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I had notes on everything I wanted to talk about, and I've managed to say it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.67,1:07:38.21,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.76,1:07:40.90,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.90,1:07:46.52,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you for sticking with me for so long. The "Run, Deliver" 3DMV
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.52,1:07:50.20,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,is also out, so please check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.72,1:07:51.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, sorry, I got that wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.92,1:07:53.08,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,2D?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.88,1:07:59.78,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The 2DMV was just uploaded to the official YouTube channel, so please go watch it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.78,1:08:00.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,It was the 2DMV.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.80,1:08:01.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.56,1:08:03.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Please check it out!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.60,1:08:11.46,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Both the 2DMV and the 3DMV... let me rephrase.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.46,1:08:23.60,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Both the 3DMV and the 2DMV for "Run, Deliver" were just released on the official YouTube channel.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.80,1:08:28.36,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm always getting so flustered. My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.52,1:08:30.56,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.56,1:08:34.90,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Once this stream is over, please watch them as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.90,1:08:36.18,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.18,1:08:37.14,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.14,1:08:38.28,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.92,1:08:40.22,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Everyone's saying they're going to watch it.
Comment: 0,1:08:40.22,1:08:41.54,Shizuku,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.22,1:08:41.54,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.54,1:08:52.76,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,And with that, it's time to wrap up this edition of ProSeka AfterTalk: "Glow Glorious Glow" edition!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.76,1:08:55.42,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,To everyone watching the stream, how did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.42,1:09:01.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Wow, seeing all your supportive comments has made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.24,1:09:04.92,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Momojan is just the best, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.56,1:09:08.50,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,They just keep on growing more and more.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.50,1:09:13.96,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Growth without a ceiling is truly dazzling to witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.68,1:09:18.40,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Thank you all so much, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.40,1:09:19.30,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I had so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.30,1:09:20.68,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,I really did.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.48,1:09:26.38,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, about "Glow Glorious Glow"... that's a bit of a tongue twister!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.38,1:09:38.22,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,If you haven't finished reading "Glow Glorious Glow" yet, you can read it all in the Event Stories menu once the next event starts.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.22,1:09:40.72,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,So please, read it over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.72,1:09:47.46,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,The scenes I mentioned earlier that we didn't get to watch together today are all in there,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.46,1:09:51.80,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,so I'd be happy if you think, "Oh, Hon-chan mentioned this part!" while you're reading.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.32,1:09:53.44,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Please check it out!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.56,1:09:59.42,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Well then, thank you all so much for sticking with me today.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.42,1:10:01.26,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,See you again next time!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.26,1:10:02.00,Shizuku,host,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
